room_title: Escape room "Tales of the Ghostly Galleon" by Hourglass Escapes in Seattle
room_description: Famed oceanographer Jacques Cousteaudian has been trapped on the legendary Ghost ship of the Banshee Buccaneer. You have just 60 minutes to help Jacques break the Buccaneers curse before he sinks with the ship and becomes a disembodied deckhand and swabs the poop-deck for eternity!
